('game-015', 'Clair Obscur: Expedition 33', 'JRPG francés con sistema de combate por turnos y mundo estilo fantasía inspirado en la Belle Époque.', 'https://external-content.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvgjournal.net%2Fmedia%2Fuploads%2Fgames%2Fimages%2F2025%2F04-April%2F18%2Fclair-obscur-expedition-33__cover__library_600x900_2x.jpg&f=1&nofb=1&ipt=b7532c2f7f5de548f66fd19a396dfc76e1f0daf9863eeb503fa54abc21da00cb', '2025-04-24', ARRAY['RPG', 'JRPG', 'Aventura'], ARRAY['PS5', 'Xbox Series X|S', 'PC'], 95, 88, 'Top 2020-2025', NOW(), NOW()),
